description:
Jazz music legend CHICO HAMILTON talks about inspiration + his new CD,TWELVE TONES OF LOVE in this exclusive portrait.  At 88 years of age, this innovative West Coast drummer has not missed a beat.  Camera Craig Carpenter & Mike D.  Chico's official website is www.joyousshout.com
